      "cookedHtml": "<h2><a name=\"p-247389-new-feature-built-in-signature-capture-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-247389-new-feature-built-in-signature-capture-1\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=15\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> New Feature: Built-In Signature Capture</h2>\n<p>Send and sign documents directly inside <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> — no external tools needed.</p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-247389-end-to-end-document-workflows-now-complete-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-247389-end-to-end-document-workflows-now-complete-2\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/writing_hand.png?v=15\" title=\":writing_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":writing_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> End-to-End Document Workflows, Now Complete</h3>\n<p>DocCreate now enables you to <strong>generate, send, and capture signatures</strong> on documents — all within your <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> boards.</p>\n<p>Eliminate tool-switching and manage everything in one place.</p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-247389-what-you-can-do-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-247389-what-you-can-do-3\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/high_voltage.png?v=15\" title=\":high_voltage:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":high_voltage:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> What You Can Do</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Send documents for signature instantly<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Capture legally binding signatures<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Track signing status in real time<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Automate signature requests using board automations</p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-247389-how-it-works-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-247389-how-it-works-4\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/counterclockwise_arrows_button.png?v=15\" title=\":counterclockwise_arrows_button:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":counterclockwise_arrows_button:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> How It Works</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Generate your document from your <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> board</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Send it for signature in one click</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Recipient signs from any device</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Status updates automatically on your board</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-247389-ideal-for-5\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-247389-ideal-for-5\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/briefcase.png?v=15\" title=\":briefcase:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":briefcase:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Ideal For</h3>\n<p>Contracts • Agreements • HR Documents • Client Approvals • Vendor Forms</p>\n<p>Perfect for teams in real estate, construction, HR, legal, finance, and operations.</p>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-247389-why-it-matters-6\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-247389-why-it-matters-6\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=15\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Why It Matters</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>No more third-party e-sign tools</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Faster approvals and deal closures</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Fully centralized document workflows</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Scales with high-volume operations</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3><a name=\"p-247389-get-started-7\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-247389-get-started-7\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/link.png?v=15\" title=\":link:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":link:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Get Started</h3>\n<p>Start sending and signing documents without leaving <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji only-emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><a href=\"https://tidycal.com/1x2y0nm/30-minute-meeting\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Schedule a Support Session</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@DocCreate\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Watch Our Tutorials on YouTube</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji only-emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><a href=\"https://support@doccrete.io\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Email</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_right.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" class=\"emoji only-emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_right:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><a href=\"https://www.doccreate.io\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Website</a></p>"
